---

<p>A <code>TreeList</code> gives the root <code>&lt;ul&gt;</code>
  <code>role="tree"</code> and gives nested <code>&lt;ul&gt;</code>s
  <code>role="group"</code> (via <code>nested: true</code>).
  Screen readers expose the hierarchy to assistive tech.</p>

<p>See the <a href="/components/tree-nav/">Tree Nav demo</a>
  for a composed example.</p>
